      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ETERNAL (1) won well in town at Caulfield Heath two back, failing to back it up last time when tackling a BM74 at Sandown Lakeside, in the market there but battling into sixth. Comes back a notch here, Zahra hops aboard and she rates to win. HOT CHIPS (2) is coming off a soft victory at Cranbourne in BM66 company, well ridden out in front there to go on and score by 1.75 lengths. Expect Stackhouse to lead again and she'll take plenty of catching from there. YOOMEE WONDER (4) is also coming off a win, too good at Ararat for easier opposition. She's still got some upside and can measure up. INTO YOU (6) will find this easier than the Country Oaks at Ballarat last time and can improve.",
